caption:
‼️Do you struggle with controlling frizz in cleaner updo styles?

This is the second updo that I taught at my latest masterclass, and I shared with my students how to layer products and smooth frizz as they work. That’s the key! Smooth and tame as you go, because spraying it with finishing hairspray will never do the trick! 🙅🏼‍♀️

I loved sharing product knowledge with my students and seeing them have those “light bulb” moments! 🙌🏻💡 

P.S. if you don’t have Aquage Spray Wax in your kit… WHAT ARE YOU DOING?! It’s literally magic frizz control in a can! 🤩

